name: steel production, electric, low-alloyed | heat, district or industrial, other than natural gas | Cutoff, U
description:
ecoQuery: https://ecoquery.ecoinvent.org/3.10/cutoff/dataset/23524/documentation

This activity represents the production of secondary low-alloyed steel in an electric arc furnace (EAF). The process comprises the following operations: 1) mixing and pretreatment (if required) of ferrous materials (including alloying additions), principally ferrous scrap; 2) furnace charging and scrap melting; 3) steel and scrap tapping; 4) secondary metallurgical treatment in a ladle furnace; and 5) casting (continuous and/or ingot).;The data are a weighted average of the regional datasets covering the following geographies: Europe without Switzerland and Austria, IN, CH, AT, CA-QC.;[This dataset is meant to replace the following datasets:; - steel production, electric, low-alloyed, GLO, 2013 - 2023 (cdf2646d-f416-4155-894a-151671ae69f6)]

At the gate of the steelmaking plant with the arrival of the ferrous scrap.

At the gate of the steelmaking plant with the cast steel ready for transport to manufacturers and fabricators.
category: C:Manufacturing/24:Manufacture of basic metals/241:Manufacture of basic iron and steel/2410:Manufacture of basic iron and steel

processDocumentation.timeDescription: The time period covers the time period of the regional datasets.
processDocumentation.geographyDescription: This dataset is a weighted average built from the following geographies: Europe without Switzerland and Austria, IN, CH, AT, CA-QC.
processDocumentation.technologyDescription: Average technology mix of the technologies used in the regional datasets.
processDocumentation.dataTreatmentDescription:
This dataset was built as a weighted average of regional datasets of the same activityName.  Weights are based on production volumes.
Europe without Switzerland and Austria: production volume = 1.12e+10 kg/year, weight = 0.6161
IN: production volume = 4.96e+09 kg/year, weight = 0.2735
CH: production volume = 1.5e+09 kg/year, weight = 0.08266
AT: production volume = 4.17e+08 kg/year, weight = 0.02297
CA-QC: production volume = 8.58e+07 kg/year, weight = 0.00473
